                       <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">On the right-hand side of the linen there are some dark stains, outside the written area. One of them is just to the right of line 1. On the left-hand side, especially towards the top, a piece of linen is missing so that the beginning of the Greek lines and the end of line 4 (of the Demotic text) have disappeared. The bottom of the linen is also damaged (in the middle and at the right-hand corner), but here no writing is lost. There are hardly any holes in the Greek text, but rather a large one in the last (Demotic) line. </ab>
                       </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                          <ab type="lines">5 lines on the front: the first 3 lines in Greek, the last 2 lines in Demotic</ab>
                          <ab type="recto-verso">Back is empty</ab>
                        </layout>
